2020–2024
Brigham Young University - Idaho

Bachelor of Science in Accounting

Certificate in Data Science

Mentorship Officer, Student Accounting Society




2025
Top Accounting Graduate





Brigham Young University - Idaho
September 2021 – April 2025 · Rexburg, ID
Courses: ACCTG 205, ACCTG 233, ACCTG 401

Helped students master key QuickBooks software functionalities

Provided detailed feedback and clarification on Excel models

Collaborated weekly with the instructor to foster an engaging learning environment




Spudnik Equipment Co.
July 2024 – September 2024 · Blackfoot, ID

Brigham Young University - Idaho

Northern RNA Inc

Recorded invoices and resolved discrepancies with AP clerks

Co-developed an inventory workflow system using Dynamics 365







The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints
June 2019 – March 2020 · Montreal, QC

Adhered to a structured schedule involving diverse responsibilities

Worked in both team and solo environments, adapting every 6 weeks

Developed communication and interpersonal skills in high-pressure environments
